<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4951920>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 7. Pherusa mikacae n. sp. A. Holotype (NHMR 17740), anterior end, dorsal view. B. Paratype (NHMR 17741), anterior end exposed, ventral view (palps corrugated, branchiae smooth). C. Paratype (ECOSUR), anterior end, dorsal view. D. Same, ventral view. E. Same, anterior region, ventral view. F. Parapodium 12, notochaetae (inset: basal, medial and distal regions). G. Same, parapodium 12, neurochaetae with eroded tips (inset: paratype NHMR 17742, parapodium 10, tip of neurohook). Scale bars: A: 0.9 mm, B: 0.8 mm, C, E: 0.7 mm, D: 1.3 mm, F: 160 µm, G: 80 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4951920/files/figure.png" .

